arch book_clasp
name The Mines of Morgria
msg
   The dwarves mined much mithril and
gems from the ancient mines of
morgria,they contributed greatly to
the prosperity of Erthos. 
  But one day...an evil creature came
to Erthos. This vile being brought
with him hordes of evil orcs and
demons. The dwarves lost their
minds,as is the curse of all
adventurers who enter the accursed
place. But,it is said that there is
one way to survive the power of the
evil thing... But what it is,I do not
know. It is said,however,that the
thing guards great treasure.
endmsg
