arch tome
name The Great Wyrms of Erthos - part 1
msg
 Many years ago,a great mother dragon
came to Erthos. This was before our
great city was founded... In the days
when the necromancer first came to
Erthos.
 The mother dragon found a fortress
build into a mountain,the fortress of
the ancient king Fraguelt whom legends
speak of. The dwarves,having never
fought dragons before,fell quickly to
her firery breath and her fierce
claws. Of the two thousand dwarves
inhabiting the great citadel,only
eight hundred escaped into the
surrounding country and lived to tell
the story.
 Thus,the dragon queen took the
mountain and bore her young. Three male
dragons;one of firery doom,one of icy
death,and one of thundering power.
These three became the leaders of the
rest of the children. 
   End of part 1...
endmsg
x 7
y 14
end
