arch tome
name The Great Wyrms of Erthos - part 2
msg
  But the three sons of the Dragon
Mother were not seen powerful enough
by her. So she asked lord Ruggilly to
grant her sons a portion of his power.
The god of chaos denied her five
times,until,he succumbed to her
constant begging. The firery
lord,greatly annoyed,granted her her
wish. But warned her,"What you have
asked of me has been granted,but you
will regret your disires. Your sons
will be immensly powerful,but they
will not remember you as they should."
  The three sons,now given a portion
of ruggilly's power,changed greatly in
appearence. But being,immensly
strong,seized their mother and cast
her in the deepest,darkest part of the
mountain. They chained her in chains
of thick adamantium,and casted spells
to weaken her and control her. She was
forced to give birth to followers of
the three sons. The sons,given great
artifacts of power by
ruggilli,pillaged the land.
Finnaly,the king of erthos,offered the
sons tribute. The three mighty dragon
lords demanded much,however,reducing
great Erthos to a meer shadow of its
former glory. The people of erthos
have prayed long for a hero to defeat
the wyrms,but so far none has come.
   
endmsg
