    You quickely flip through the book.
 Your eye glances on a page... It's
 about the Necromancer...
___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.
   Today is proclaimed a day of
celebration! The necromancer has been
defeated,his tower has been
demolished. The hero who slayed
him,Urrgos,has been proclaimed
Champion of the King! I go now to
enjoy myself in the celebration.
___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.
  This is dreadful... The necromancer
 has appeared once again,it seems he's
 back from the dead. His undead have
 been summoned,noone is safe in the
 land. The town of Dun Agotha has been
 destroyed,only the grand castle of
 the town remains untouched among the
 ruins. The hero Urrgos is not to be
 found.
.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.___.
  It seems Urrgos has joined with the
 necromancer,he killed the king in his
 own court. Stunned nobles did not
 raise the alarm,until it was too
 late. The king has been slain. I
 myself am dying of battle wounds. A
 group of skeletons surrounded my
 company,we fought bravely,but i shall
 not live to see the king's son take
 the crown. I leave my diary to
 whomever may find it...
endmsg
